      • ConferencePaper

        public ConferencePaper(java.lang.String[] scholars,
               java.lang.String title,
               java.lang.String serialTitle,
               java.lang.String[] pageNumbers,
               java.lang.String date,
               java.lang.String digitalIdentifier)
        This constructor initializes all of the variables specific to a ConferencePaper.
        Parameters:
        scholars - an array of the scholar's names for this conference paper. The first scholar should be the primary one.
        title - the title of this conference paper.
        serialTitle - the title of the serial publishing this conference paper.
        pageNumbers - an array representing the first and last page numbers in the serial where this conference paper is found.
        date - the date this conference paper was published.
        digitalIdentifier - a digital identifier for the conference paper such as a URL.
        Conditions:
        POST - all instance variables are initialized.
